## Curl to order a VSI with metadata and an sshkey specified 
'{"parameters":[{"blockDevices":[{"device":0,"diskImage":{"capacity":"100"}}],"userData":[{"value":"ghapi=d20087d60c2d9dad41654f4408dbfd78b5b79350"}],"sshKeys":[{"id":187111}],"datacenter"{"name":"hou02"},"domain":"tinybot.io","hourlyBillingFlag":true,"localDiskFlag":false,"maxMemory":"2","hostname":"apitest","startCpus":"2","operatingSystemReferenceCode":"UBUNTU_LATEST_64"}]}'

## Get all VSI's on an account. Just need account ID
curl -s -k -u https://$api_user:$api_key@api.softlayer.com/rest/v3/SoftLayer_User_Customer/ACCOUNT_ID/getVirtualGuests?objectMask=mask[id,blockDevices[id,diskImage[id,capacity]]]
